casebody.data:
CITY OF CIBOLO, TEXAS, petitioner,
v.
GREEN VALLEY SPECIAL UTILITY DISTRICT. No. 17-938. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2019.

Motion of Guadalupe Valley Development Corporation, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
